 13  /-- A `ctop α σ` is a realization of a topology (basis) on `α`,
 14    represented by a type `σ` together with operations for the top element and
 15    the intersection operation. -/
 16  structure ctop (α σ : Type*) :=
id                         └───┘
typ                        └───┘

typ         ┴ ┴ ┴
 19  (top_mem : ∀ x : α, x ∈ f (top x))
id                ┴   ┴  ┴ ┴ ┴  └─┘ ┴
src                        ┴
typ               ┴   ┴  ┴ ┴ ┴  └─┘ ┴
 20  (inter : Π a b (x : α), x ∈ f a ∩ f b → σ)
